---
name: v21-native-constructor-pattern-alternative
---

```scalascript
case class A(value: Int)
case class B(value: Int)

def classify(value: Any): String =
  value match
    case A(_) | B(_) => "hit"
    case _ => "miss"

println(classify(A(1)))
println(classify(B(2)))
println(classify("other"))
```
